query:
WITH exist AS (
            SELECT *
            FROM pgmq.q_build_queue
            WHERE MESSAGE ->> 'container_name' = $1
            ),
            inserted AS (
                INSERT INTO builds (id, project_id)
                SELECT $2, $3
                WHERE NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM exist)
                RETURNING id
            )
            SELECT pgmq.send('build_queue', $4::jsonb) 
            FROM inserted;
